com.morpheus.sdk.provisioning

Class ServicePlan

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.morpheus.sdk.provisioning.ServicePlan

  • public class ServicePlan
extends java.lang.Object
    A Model representation of a Morpheus Service Plan It is used by GSON Decoder to convert JSON of the following structure into a java based Object. 
     "plan": {
                "account": null,
                "active": true,
                "class": "com.morpheus.ServicePlan",
                "code": "container-512",
                "configs": null,
                "dateCreated": "2015-09-18T22:46:21Z",
                "description": "Memory: 512MB Storage: 5GB",
                "editable": true,
                "externalCost": null,
                "externalId": null,
                "id": 223,
                "internalCost": null,
                "internalId": null,
                "lastUpdated": "2015-10-07T23:46:11Z",
                "layouts": [
                        {
                                "class": "com.morpheus.InstanceTypeLayout",
                                "id": 23
                        },
                        {
                                "class": "com.morpheus.InstanceTypeLayout",
                                "id": 48
                        }
                ],
                "maxCpu": null,
                "maxLog": null,
                "maxMemory": 536870912,
                "maxStorage": 5368709120,
                "name": "Memory: 512MB Storage: 5GB",
                "serverType": null,
                "sortOrder": 2,
                "upgradeable": false,
                "visibility": "public"
        }
